</details>

If `$ webchatgpt` doesn't look cool on you, there's this workaround `python -m WebChatGPT`

Starting from [v0.2.4](https://github.com/Simatwa/WebChatGPT/releases) onwards, shortcut to `$ webchatgpt` is `$ wbc`.

